Uses of Package
org.activebpel.wsio

Packages that use org.activebpel.wsio
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel Root package for the Active Endpoints Runtime for Axis (rtaxis).  
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.handlers Handlers translate between messages and protocol formats such as JAX-RPC or SOAP Document.  
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.invokers Contains impls of the actual rpc or document style invokers used to call out to external web services.  
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.rdebug.server Contains all server module for the ActiveBPEL remote administration and debug Web Services. 
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.receivers   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel This package contains classes for creating a BPEL model and for implements a standalone BPEL engine for testing designs. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl This package contains the base classes used in the implementation model for the BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.addressing   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.endpoints Endpoint reference factory, serializer, and deserializer.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.queue Contains classes that model inbound and outbound messages from the engine as well as alarms.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.storage Classes related to saving and restoring the state of processes.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.addressing Handles partner addressing (finding the correct endpoint reference for a given business partner).  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.admin Classes that manage queued receives and a bean that holds deployed process information.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.admin.rdebug.server   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine The BPEL engine, support classes, and engine factory.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.invoke   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.receive   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery This package contains classes for recovering or regenerating the state of a process from alarms, messages, or faults that the process received. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.reply   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage This package contains classes for storing the state of BPEL processes to an external storage facility. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.wsio.invoke   
org.activebpel.wsio Root package for the Active Endpoints external web service and invoke classes. 
org.activebpel.wsio.invoke Provides interfaces and classes for external invocation layer. 
org.activebpel.wsio.receive
